#

Crispy Lemon Garlic Butter Shrimp

$18.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

SeafoodQuick MealFamily-Friendly

Description

Succulent shrimp sautéed in a zesty garlic butter sauce with a hint of lemon, served over a bed of fluffy rice.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp: 1 lb, peeled and deveined
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Lemon: 1, juiced and zested
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Red Pepper Flakes: 1/2 tsp, optional
  • Rice: 1 cup, cooked
